Package: ggCorpIdent
Title: INWTlab wrapper for ggplot2 to create plots matching a corporate identity
Version: 0.9.1
Author: INWT Statistics GmbH
Authors@R: c(person("Mira CÃ©line", "Klein", email = "mira.klein@inwt-statistics.de", role = c("aut")),
             person("Steffen", "Wagner", email = "steffen.wagner@inwt-statistics.de", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: This R package provides a wrapper for ggplot2 suitable for building business
  graphs in your corporate design. A logo can be added to the graph and you can easily customize colors, fonts, etc..
  Since customization takes place on a global level, the ggplot syntax itself remains unchanged and doesn't need to be touched. 
BugReports: https://github.com/INWTlab/ggCorpIdent/issues
URL: http://github.com/INWTlab/ggCorpIdent
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0),
    extrafont (>= 0.17),
    ggplot2 (>= 3.0.0)
Imports: png(>= 0.1.7),
Suggests: extrafontdb (>= 1.0), knitr, rmarkdown
